&lt;Majestic Electronic Stores Inc> saidit intends to make a normal course issuer bid to purchase up tofive pct of its 5.2 mln outstanding common shares on the openmarket during the 12 month period commencing April 13, 1987.    The company said the purpose of the proposed issuer bid isto avoid possible dilution of share value under a proposedemployee stock option plan.    Majestic expects to have its employee stock option plan inplace during the year, it said. Reuter&#3;